protobuf:compile

Full name:

net.chwthewke.maven.protobuf:maven-protobuf-plugin:0.1.5:compile

Description:

Goal which executes the protoc compiler.

Attributes:

  • Requires a Maven project to be executed.
  • Binds by default to the lifecycle phase: generate-sources.

Optional Parameters

Name Type Since Description
protoPaths String[] - (no description)
protocExecutable Dependency - (no description)
protocPlugins ProtocPlugin[] - The plugins to execute with their respective output directories.
protocolDependencies Dependency[] - (no description)
protocolSourceDependencies Dependency[] - (no description)
sourceDirectories String[] - The source directories of the protocol. Default: ${basedir}/src/main/proto
